jsonparser

Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsonparser.Parser

  • public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    Mikko Json Parser Object for storing and writing json-data. User can store key-value pairs in object. Can also store other parser-objects data as sub-objects.
    Since:
    1.0
